{"tid":2184541,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實喺咪無辦法幫到 12位手足？","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T01:05:50.000Z","uid":348759,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb374ff229c98d55dd8ee8ce7eff8197ce68d43d","tid":2184541,"uid":348759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<br />\n自8月23日手足被捕送中，至今已過九日。根據報道，目前手足處於深圳鹽田看守所遭受扣留。然而，不論中國及港府至今仍未交代被捕港人所涉嫌罪名，會否起訴等詳情。<br />\n<br />\n羈押期間不同：刑事拘留<span class=\"pink\">一般為14日</span>，對流竄作案、多次作案、結伙作案的重大嫌疑分子的<span class=\"pink\">最長拘留期限為37日</span>。<br />\n<br />\n這一個月對手足對家屬而言非常關鍵，<br />\n大家的關注能催促香港政府盡快回應，<br />\n所以務必繼續關注聲援，<br />\n無論以什麼形式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願手足平安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0pENhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0pENhR.png&h=e263c122&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5581c0acb3b17947c8928ccaa8fe82521e1eda3f","tid":2184541,"uid":348759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648c5417e03c1f68533fb18332badebb6b2b4205","tid":2184541,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"被捕位係咪公公水域<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明佢地係出境<br />\n點解會被「入境管轄權」中國送中<br />\n<br />\n即係洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繞過香港送中<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣書店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0358968a9a09d099e104cb575f3241e678567374","tid":2184541,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"648c5417e03c1f68533fb18332badebb6b2b4205","tid":2184541,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"被捕位係咪公公水域<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明佢地係出境<br />\n點解會被「入境管轄權」中國送中<br />\n<br />\n即係洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繞過香港送中<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣書店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"最初消息流出好似係用「偷渡」呢個字眼<br />\n<br />\n點講都唔通唔應該係送中國拘留 佢地都唔係偷渡「入」中國<br />\n<br />\n退一萬步都應該係遣返香港拘留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係咪佢地一直唔肯公布咩原因拘留嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4596f534a43e8befb82c1a2d1fb05a1750d7da1d","tid":2184541,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"感謝你幫手開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13244b042cb9d32e00c8fef069ec28f78ef34d4f","tid":2184541,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69f09d1bf518feae6fa60189bda559b14ff1e5e","tid":2184541,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"政府幾時回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795af4d94a5b121c6c6e545ec5b5d675abf54ea6","tid":2184541,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/